arCallbacks.szOnCallbackCompleteScript:
function Start(idActorPlayer, sWorldName)

	idDoor = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_ByThree_BreakableDoor")[1]
	tGhoulSpawners1 = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_ByThree_GhoulWave1Spawners")
	tGhoulSpawners2 = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_ByThree_GhoulWave2Spawners")
	
	Hydra.ActorSetInvulnerable(idDoor, true)
	Hydra.ActorSetTargetable(idDoor, false)
	Hydra.MusicOverride("QST_Hawe_EliasQuest", "Music_Hawezar_FA-DNG_Low")
end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

	Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(convAtDoor, idActor)
	Hydra.WaitForConversationFinished(convAtDoor)
	Hydra.ActorSetInvulnerable(idDoor, false)
	Hydra.ActorSetTargetable(idDoor, true)
	Hydra.ActorSetDamageCap(idDoor, 0.65)
	Hydra.MusicOverride("QST_Hawe_EliasQuest", "Music_Hawezar_FA-DNG_Hi")
end

function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)

	locFakeFlippy = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idActorGizmo, "markerloc")[1]
	tPlayers = Hydra.PlayerActorsInLevelArea("QST_Hawe_EliasQuest_Boss")
	
	for i, PlayerID in ipairs(tPlayers) do
		Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(locFakeFlippy, fxJournalFlippy, false, idSelf)
	end
	
	Hydra.ActorsEnableLinkedByActorInGroup(idActorGizmo, "journal")

end

function Start(idActor, flPrevHP, flHp)

	tPlayers = Hydra.PlayerActorsInLevelArea(S_LEVELAREA_BOSS_ARENA)
	
	for i, Player in ipairs(tPlayers) do
		Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(convLilith1, Player)
	end

end

function Start(idActor, flPrevHP, flHp)

	tPlayers = Hydra.PlayerActorsInLevelArea(S_LEVELAREA_BOSS_ARENA)
	
	for i, Player in ipairs(tPlayers) do
		Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(convLilith2, Player)
	end

end

function Start(idActor, flPrevHP, flHp)

	tPlayers = Hydra.PlayerActorsInLevelArea(S_LEVELAREA_BOSS_ARENA)
	
	for i, Player in ipairs(tPlayers) do
		Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(convLilith3, Player)
	end

end

function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)

	Hydra.BossEncounterManuallyComplete(S_LEVELAREA_BOSS_ARENA)
	Hydra.ActorEnable(idSymonCorpse)
	Hydra.ActorDisable(idSymonProp)
	Hydra.MusicOverride("QST_Hawe_EliasQuest", "Music_Hawezar_FA-DNG_Boss-Victory")
end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

	idSymonCorpse = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idActorDetector, "corpse_chest")[1]
	idSymonProp = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idActorDetector, "corpse_prop")[1]
	
	-- Only want the line to play once even on boss reset
	if bEnteredRoom == false then
		Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(convEnterGateRoom, idActor)
		Hydra.WaitForConversationFinished(convEnterGateRoom)
		Hydra.Wait(1)
		bEnteredRoom = true
	end
	
	Hydra.BossEncounterManuallyQueueStart(S_LEVELAREA_BOSS_ARENA)
Hydra.MusicOverride("QST_Hawe_EliasQuest", "Music_Hawezar_FA-DNG_Boss")
end

function Start(idActor, flPrevHP, flHp)

	idDoor = idActor
	idBloodLoc = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idDoor, "bloodloc")[1]
	idBloodWallLoc = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idDoor, "bloodwallloc")[1]
	Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectSize(idBloodLoc, 8)
	Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectSize(idBloodWallLoc, 2.5)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idBloodLoc, fxBloodBurst)
	Hydra.ActorTriggerPowerAtFeet(idDoor, powerKnockback)
	Hydra.ActorSetInvulnerable(idDoor, true)
	Hydra.ActorSetTargetable(idDoor, false)

	for i, Spawner in ipairs(tGhoulSpawners1) do
		Hydra.ActorEnable(Spawner)
	end
	
	Hydra.Wait(1)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idBloodWallLoc, fxBloodWall, true)
	
end

function Start(idActor, flPrevHP, flHp)

	idDoor = idActor
	idBloodLoc = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idDoor, "bloodloc")[1]
	idBloodWallLoc = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idDoor, "bloodwallloc")[1]
	Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectSize(idBloodWallLoc, 2.5)
	Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectSize(idBloodLoc, 8)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idBloodLoc, fxBloodBurst)
	Hydra.ActorTriggerPowerAtFeet(idDoor, powerKnockback)
	Hydra.ActorSetInvulnerable(idDoor, true)
	Hydra.ActorSetTargetable(idDoor, false)
	
	for i, Spawner in ipairs(tGhoulSpawners2) do
		Hydra.ActorEnable(Spawner)
	end
	
	Hydra.Wait(1)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idBloodWallLoc, fxBloodWall, true)
	
end

arCallbackSets.szOnSetCompleteScript:
Hydra.ActorRemoveComplexEffectByEffectGroupSNO(idBloodWallLoc, fxBloodWall)
Hydra.ActorSetInvulnerable(idDoor, false)
Hydra.ActorSetTargetable(idDoor, true)
Hydra.ActorSetDamageCap(idDoor, 0.32)
Hydra.QuestAdvancePhase()

Hydra.ActorRemoveComplexEffectByEffectGroupSNO(idBloodWallLoc, fxBloodWall)
Hydra.ActorSetInvulnerable(idDoor, false)
Hydra.ActorSetTargetable(idDoor, true)
Hydra.ActorSetDamageCap(idDoor, 0)
Hydra.QuestAdvancePhase()
